{
  "stem": "3040.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there's nothing else in between because the people, the young people, even though they may have been bored, staying home or always learning, but they couldn't do anything else because of the restrictions put on them by families in the type of families that I come from.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I personally, I would say-- before we go through this, I want to continue with one other holiday, which is very important holiday, Sukkot.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why's it important?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we really lived in the sukkah at this time, during the eight days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some slept in the sukkah also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had all our meals in the sukkah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we spent all of free time in the sukkah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The sukkah was, was a temporary home, which was made so comfortable that you really-- it was protected from the rain because we had these opening, the roofs.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In case it was raining, we could close the roof over it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But while the roof was down, you are not allowed to eat there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You could eat in the sukkah only when the roof was up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you were exposed to just the covering of, of the-- of the sukkah.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we used to decorate the sukkah so magnificently, like it was like a castle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You would have all kinds of figures, made of different colored paper hanging on the wall and hanging from the-- from the roof.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the young people, I myself, used to spend weeks and weeks before Sukkot preparing all of these decoration.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a very special time because we were really into it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we took great pleasure and great pride in doing it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now you were asking me--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I personally, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we-- actually, here you would describe it the upper middle class.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
